column1: Outsourcing staff: Added 1 new staff member from October 2024
Added the Move in January at a Cost of $150,000
Added a BD in from January 2025 at a cost of $190k p.a.
Deducted the Chemist salary for July 2024 and started in August 2024
Added Depreciation from Jan for new Plant & Equipment @ 15% p.a. for $1mil cost
Added Depreciation from cost of build @ 2.5% p.a. for $5.8mil cost
Borrowing costs are based on actual figure paid per month from July to Dec 2024
Borrowing costs are based on a principal debt of $7mil & interest @ 7%p.a. for Jan to June 2025
